 without sensational curiosity? Anguished and unflinchingly honest, as eloquent as it is raw and painful, Evil Men asks hard questions about the most disturbing capabilities human beings possess, and acknowledges that these questions may have no comforting answers.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 08. Jul 2019) 4aPHILOSOPHY / Ethics & Moral Philosophy. 4aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Political Freedom & Security / Human Rights. 7aHISTORY / Military / World War II.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2013z9783110317350oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE HISTORY, POLITICAL SCIENCE, SOCIOLOGY  2013z978311031712108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET GESCHICHTE, POLITIKWISS., SOZIOLOGIE  2013z9783110317114oZDB-23-DPS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP Complete eBook Package 2011-2014z978311037488908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP eBook Package 2013z978311037490208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP eBook Package Backlist 2000-2013z978311044220508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP eBook Package Backlist 2000-2014z978311045951708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP eBook Package Backlist 2000-2015z978311066256640uhttps://doi.org/10.4159/harvard.9780674073975423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780674073975.jpg  a978-3-11-031712-1  E-BOOK PACKAGE HISTORY, POLITICAL SCIENCE, SOCIOLOGY  2013b2013  a978-3-11-037488-9  HUP Complete eBook Package 2011-2014  a978-3-11-037490-2  HUP eBook Package 2013b2013  a978-3-11-044220-5  HUP eBook Package Backlist 2005-2013c2000d2013  a978-3-11-045951-7  HUP eBook Package Backlist 2000-2014c2000d2014  a978-3-11-066256-6  HUP eBook Package Backlist 2000-2015  aEBA_B